data.description: Rare 2 bedroom, 1 bath unit available in desirable Southwinds Condominiums. This property is walking distance to the beach with both Resident's Beach and public beach access nearby. Make this nicely updated, beautifully furnished and decorated, turnkey beachside condo your new piece of paradise. Conveniently located near restaurants, shops and entertainment. This is a must see property!
